01:01:06.310 --> 01:01:07.430
PROFESSOR: This is a 0.

01:01:07.430 --> 01:01:14.970
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
So we're only

01:01:14.970 --> 01:01:18.635
looking at nearest neighbor,
so are we essentially saying

01:01:18.635 --> 01:01:23.254
the case where i equals j is
approximately 0 [INAUDIBLE].

01:01:23.254 --> 01:01:25.045
AUDIENCE 2: Because
